PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784144490
OL,3,CAmbulance trust investigating if staff
OL,4,Caccessed Southport victims' records
OL,6,FAn ambulance trust is looking into
OL,7,Fwhether staff inappropriately accessed
OL,8,Fthe records of victims of the
OL,9,FSouthport attack.
OL,11,FNorth West Ambulance Service (NWAS)
OL,12,Fdid not inform patients or their
OL,13,Ffamilies and did not discipline staff
OL,14,Fover the matter, the HSJ reports.
OL,16,FThe father of one victim accused staff
OL,17,Fof wanting to "satisfy their own
OL,18,Fmorbid curiosity" and described the
OL,19,Fsituation as "appalling".
OL,26,@yD@OOUzD@QO]{D@NOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784144490
OL,3,CAmbulance trust investigating if staff
OL,4,Caccessed Southport victims' records
OL,6,FIt comes after it emerged in May that
OL,7,Fdozens of workers at another NHS trust
OL,8,Fhad looked at records with no good
OL,9,Freason.
OL,11,FThree girls ` Alice da Silva Aguiar,
OL,12,Fnine, Bebe King, six, and Elsie Dot
OL,13,FStancombe, seven ` were murdered by
OL,14,FAxel Rudakubana at The Hart Space,
OL,15,Fwhile 10 others were injured, in the
OL,16,Fattack in July 2024.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784144490
OL,3,CAmbulance trust investigating if staff
OL,4,Caccessed Southport victims' records
OL,6,FA March 2025 report by University
OL,7,FHospitals of Liverpool Group, which
OL,8,Fwas produced after its own staff
OL,9,Flooked at the records of victims, was
OL,10,Fobtained by the HSJ from a Freedom of
OL,11,FInformation request.
OL,13,FIt revealed 10 individuals in the
OL,14,Fambulance service may have
OL,15,Finappropriately accessed the incident.
OL,17,FAt the time it was decided it was "not
OL,18,Fappropriate" to inform the patients by
OL,19,Fthe NWAS data security lead.
OL,26,@yD@cOUzD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784144490
OL,3,CAmbulance trust investigating if staff
OL,4,Caccessed Southport victims' records
OL,6,FIt added that it would not formally
OL,7,Fdiscipline staff, but would bolster HR
OL,8,Fprocesses for future incidents.
OL,10,FNews of the probe at NWAS comes after
OL,11,Fit emerged in May that 48 staff at
OL,12,FUniversity Hospitals of Liverpool
OL,13,FGroup has accessed the records of
OL,14,FSouthport victims with no good reason.
OL,16,FAt the time, Leanne Lucas, who was the
OL,17,Finstructor at the Taylor Swift-themed
OL,18,Fdance event and is one of the three
OL,19,Fadult survivors of the attack, said
OL,20,Fshe was "devastated and horrified".
OL,26,@|D@IOU|D@bO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784144490
OL,3,CAmbulance trust investigating if staff
OL,4,Caccessed Southport victims' records
OL,6,FSpeaking of the latest potential
OL,7,Fbreach, she said: "Life has never been
OL,8,Fthe same since 29 July 2024, and so
OL,9,Fmany people are still living with the
OL,10,Ftrauma of that day.
OL,12,F"To now learn of another potential
OL,13,Fdata breach is deeply upsetting,
OL,14,Fparticularly after staff at NHS
OL,15,FUniversity Hospitals of Liverpool
OL,16,Fwrongly accessed my medical records.
OL,17,FIt feels like insult added to injury.
OL,26,@oD@SOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784144490
OL,3,CAmbulance trust investigating if staff
OL,4,Caccessed Southport victims' records
OL,6,F"You never really think about the
OL,7,Ftrust you place in public services,
OL,8,Fsuch as the ambulance service and
OL,9,Fhospitals, until you need them most.
OL,11,F"To learn that trust may have been
OL,12,Fbreached in this way is simply
OL,13,Funacceptable. I am now waiting to hear
OL,14,Ffrom North West Ambulance Service as
OL,15,Fto whether my records were accessed.
OL,17,F"Whatever the outcome, I hope there is
OL,18,Fa thorough investigation, full
OL,19,Ftransparency for everyone affected,
OL,20,Fand robust measures put in place to
OL,21,Fensure this can never happen again."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUyD@AOU}D@dO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784144490
OL,3,CAmbulance trust investigating if staff
OL,4,Caccessed Southport victims' records
OL,6,FThe father of one of the victims, who
OL,7,Fwas just 13 when she was treated at
OL,8,FAintree Hospital for a stab wound to
OL,9,Fthe back, said: "It is a complete
OL,10,Fbreach of trust in our darkest hours
OL,11,Fas a family and dampens how you feel
OL,12,Fabout the amazing work they do to save
OL,13,Flives.
OL,26,@qD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784144490
OL,3,CAmbulance trust investigating if staff
OL,4,Caccessed Southport victims' records
OL,6,F"It was already incredibly difficult
OL,7,Fto think that staff at Aintree
OL,8,FHospital had needlessly pried into our
OL,9,Fdaughter's condition, but to then
OL,10,Flearn that ambulance staff have done
OL,11,Fthe same and we have only found out by
OL,12,Fraking through these documents is
OL,13,Fappalling.
OL,15,F"They weren't checking on her
OL,16,Fcondition, they just wanted to satisfy
OL,17,Ftheir own morbid curiosity.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784144490
OL,3,CAmbulance trust investigating if staff
OL,4,Caccessed Southport victims' records
OL,6,F"The Trusts are still unable to tell
OL,7,Fus with certainty whether photographs
OL,8,Fof our daughter's injuries were viewed
OL,9,Fby staff, so we don't know what to
OL,10,Fbelieve.
OL,12,F"The decision to share what happened
OL,13,Fto her should have been our daughter's
OL,14,Fto make, now nobody can guarantee what
OL,15,Fdata was shared and retained.
OL,17,F"They've had multiple chances to tell
OL,18,Fus about this but instead we have been
OL,19,Fleft to discover it all two years
OL,20,Flater, when we should be focusing on
OL,21,Frecovering and moving forward."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUyD@AOU}D@_O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784144490
OL,3,CAmbulance trust investigating if staff
OL,4,Caccessed Southport victims' records
OL,6,FSalman Desai, NWAS chief executive,
OL,7,Fsaid: "We have identified concerns
OL,8,Fabout potential inappropriate access
OL,9,Fto patient records and are formally
OL,10,Finvestigating the matter.
OL,12,F"We will contact families and patients
OL,13,Fwho may have been affected as our
OL,14,Finquiries progress. Any inappropriate
OL,15,Faccess to patient information will be
OL,16,Ftreated extremely seriously.
OL,18,F"We are deeply sorry for the concern
OL,19,Fand distress this may cause."
OL,26,@oD@GOUtD@AOUzD@AOU{D@]O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784144490
OL,3,CAmbulance trust investigating if staff
OL,4,Caccessed Southport victims' records
OL,6,FNicola Ryan-Donnelly, associate
OL,7,Fsolicitor at Fletchers Solicitors,
OL,8,Fsaid: "The recent string of patient
OL,9,Fdata breaches has shown there is a
OL,10,Fdeep-rooted culture of snooping within
OL,11,Fthe NHS.
OL,13,F"People who are seriously injured or
OL,14,Fdying should not have the added worry
OL,15,Fthat they are being pried on, as they
OL,16,Fare rushed into hospital fighting for
OL,17,Ftheir lives.
OL,26,@pD@GOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784144490
OL,3,CAmbulance trust investigating if staff
OL,4,Caccessed Southport victims' records
OL,6,F"We want to see a full review by NHS
OL,7,FEngland of the current policy
OL,8,Fgoverning all NHS staff on
OL,9,Finappropriate patient data breaches."
OL,11,FThere have been a string of cases of
OL,12,FNHS staff looking at medical records
OL,13,Fwithout reason in recent months.
OL,15,FIn June, Cambridge University
OL,16,FHospitals (CUH) said it was
OL,17,Finvestigating after the medical
OL,18,Frecords of a three-year-old boy hurt
OL,19,Fin a crocodile pit were accessed by
OL,20,Faround 40 members of hospital staff.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/13
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,366,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F365A1784144490
OL,3,CAmbulance trust investigating if staff
OL,4,Caccessed Southport victims' records
OL,6,FAnd in May, Nottingham University
OL,7,FHospitals NHS Trust (NUH) said 11
OL,8,Fmembers of staff had been dismissed
OL,9,Fand a further 14 have had actions
OL,10,Ftaken against them for inappropriately
OL,11,Faccessing medical records of the
OL,12,FNottingham stabbing victims.
OL,14,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,15,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,16,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,17,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,18,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,19,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/13
